title: Papa Joe - Kebab King
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Papa Joe Falafel and Hummus was previously known as Kebab King. It's a take-away food bar. A couple of the sauces might contain dairy - ask which ones. NOTE: reported to be veg, but facebook images show meats.
